Description: SecuBox SimpleX Chat Server
 Privacy-focused SimpleX SMP/XFTP server management for SecuBox.
 .
 Features:
  - SimpleX Chat SMP relay server
  - Zero-knowledge messaging infrastructure
  - No user identifiers or metadata
  - Docker/Podman container deployment
  - TLS certificate management
  - Backup and restore functionality
  - Connection statistics
  - Queue management
 .
 SimpleX is a decentralized messaging protocol that provides
 strong privacy guarantees without relying on user identifiers.
